claim.claim-text:
1. A mobile aggregate crushing system comprising:
a plurality of crushing machines and a plurality of screening machines arranged in a configuration, so that, an output of a first crushing machine is provided to an input of a first screening machine;
each of said plurality of screening machines being configured to output material at a first common predetermined output conveyor height;
each of said plurality of crushing machines being configured to receive material thereon from an outside source at a first common predetermined feed point height; and
a plurality of conveyors, which includes at least one folding conveyor and in combination with said plurality of crushing machines and said plurality of screening machines forms a closed loop where materials can be recirculated, where each of said plurality of conveyors which extends between:
one of said plurality of crushing machines, and
one of said plurality of screening machines;

is integrated with one of a crushing machine and a screening machine; and
wherein said common predetermined output conveyor height and said common predetermined feed point height; are fixed such that an alternate operable working configuration of said plurality of screening machines and said plurality of crushing machines can be made without making any horizontal or vertical adjustments of the any of said conveyors.
